{"data":[{"book":"Yesaia","chapter":"59","verse":"1","text":"Ampa ara Awurade nsa nyɛ tiaa sɛ ɛrennye nkwa,"},{"book":"Yesaia","chapter":"59","verse":"2","text":"Nanso mo amumɔyɛ na atetew"},{"book":"Yesaia","chapter":"59","verse":"3","text":"Na mogya akeka mo nsa ho,"},{"book":"Yesaia","chapter":"59","verse":"4","text":"Obiara nhwehwɛ atɛntrenee;"},{"book":"Yesaia","chapter":"59","verse":"5","text":"Wosow nhurutoa nkesua"},{"book":"Yesaia","chapter":"59","verse":"6","text":"Wɔn ntontan nye mma adurade;"},{"book":"Yesaia","chapter":"59","verse":"7","text":"Wotu mmirika kɔyɛ bɔne;"},{"book":"Yesaia","chapter":"59","verse":"8","text":"Asomdwoe kwan no, wonnim;"},{"book":"Yesaia","chapter":"59","verse":"9","text":"Enti atɛntrenee ne yɛn ntam aware,"},{"book":"Yesaia","chapter":"59","verse":"10","text":"Te sɛ anifuraefo no, yɛkeka wɔ afasu ho"},{"book":"Yesaia","chapter":"59","verse":"11","text":"Yɛn nyinaa woro so te sɛ sisi;"},{"book":"Yesaia","chapter":"59","verse":"12","text":"Efisɛ, yɛn mfomso adɔɔso wɔ wʼani so,"},{"book":"Yesaia","chapter":"59","verse":"13","text":"atuatew ne nkontompo a etia Awurade,"},{"book":"Yesaia","chapter":"59","verse":"14","text":"Enti wɔapam atɛntrenee kɔ nʼakyi,"},{"book":"Yesaia","chapter":"59","verse":"15","text":"Nokware nni baabiara,"},{"book":"Yesaia","chapter":"59","verse":"16","text":"Ohuu sɛ obiara nni hɔ,"},{"book":"Yesaia","chapter":"59","verse":"17","text":"Ɔhyɛɛ trenee sɛ nkatabo,"},{"book":"Yesaia","chapter":"59","verse":"18","text":"Obegyina nea wɔayɛ so"},{"book":"Yesaia","chapter":"59","verse":"19","text":"Efi atɔe fam, nnipa besuro Awurade din"},{"book":"Yesaia","chapter":"59","verse":"20","text":"“Ogyefo no bɛba Sion,"},{"book":"Yesaia","chapter":"59","verse":"21","text":"“Me de, eyi yɛ me ne wɔn apam,” sɛnea Awurade se ni. “Me Honhom a ɔwɔ mo so, ne me nsɛm a mede ahyɛ mo anom, remfi mo anom, anaa mo mma, ne mo mma asefo anom, efi saa bere yi kosi daa apem,” sɛɛ na Awurade se."}]}